Within the next couple of weeks, #NFT holders will have the opportunity to reveal their base-layer trait, exposing 1 of 11 different variations.

The rarer the base layer, the higher the multiplier, which forms part of an equation to calculate how much $FLR you can claim as the owner of the NFT (every block).

Some may chose to reveal their NFT, others may refrain and keep an untouched relic, with intentions of selling at a later date for a higher price.

There will be a comprehensive tracking website to showcase live statistics of the project, including how many have been revealed and the remaining traits available.

Expect the reveal to begin sometime before Christmas.
